title: Interview: Rachel Maddow
description:
MSNBC’s Rachel Maddow chats with Seth about fighting skinheads as a teen, why Donald Trump’s international financial conflicts of interest may be worse than we expect, and the small sliver of hope Democrats can feel about Trump’s election.
